<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="14800000t" end="42800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">諾曼要出欄？</p>
<p begin="43600000t" end="69200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">沒錯，已經決定了是明天</p>
<p begin="123200000t" end="146000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">媽媽，艾瑪的腿這樣…</p>
<p begin="146800000t" end="167600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">我扭得很有技巧，沒事的</p>
<p begin="180400000t" end="197600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">康復之後會跟以前一樣</p>
<p begin="198400000t" end="209200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">不會有疤痕</p>
<p begin="210000000t" end="233200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">完全康復應該需要一至兩個月</p>
<p begin="239200000t" end="264400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">能趕及在你生日之前康復就好了</p>
<p begin="265200000t" end="272400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">阿雷</p>
<p begin="292400000t" end="301600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">你手上那個袋子</p>
<p begin="302400000t" end="319600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">一會兒記得拿來給我</p>
<p begin="334800000t" end="359200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">好，我們回去吧</p>
<p begin="471600000t" end="494800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">(還能爭取多少自由)</p>
<p begin="578400000t" end="617200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">「約定的夢幻島」</p>
<p begin="650400000t" end="659200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">(Fire)</p>
<p begin="665600000t" end="688000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">(該我出場了　率先上陣)</p>
<p begin="688800000t" end="712400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">(在知道何謂失敗之前)</p>
<p begin="713200000t" end="741200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">(先找到導火線)</p>
<p begin="742000000t" end="753600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">(朝它Fire)</p>
<p begin="754400000t" end="783600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">(沒有神明可崇拜　也沒有星星)</p>
<p begin="784400000t" end="809600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">(但是從沒放棄祈求)</p>
<p begin="810400000t" end="837200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">(因害怕後悔而停滯的腳步)</p>
<p begin="838000000t" end="848000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">(朝它Fire)</p>
<p begin="848800000t" end="896400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">(想忘記的正是無法忘掉的事)</p>
<p begin="897200000t" end="943200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">(通往天堂之路始於地獄)</p>
<p begin="944000000t" end="990800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">(一點火花化為熊熊烈火)</p>
<p begin="991600000t" end="1024400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">(緊張不安地不斷追趕)</p>
<p begin="1025200000t" end="1048800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">(奔往未來)</p>
<p begin="1049600000t" end="1071200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">(儘管只是數厘米)</p>
<p begin="1072000000t" end="1094800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">(也要朝著願望中的目的地)</p>
<p begin="1095600000t" end="1118400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">(不斷前行　不要停步)</p>
<p begin="1146400000t" end="1192800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">(為內心贖罪　勸自己放棄)</p>
<p begin="1193600000t" end="1214000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">(這樣將來還能說甚麼)</p>
<p begin="1240400000t" end="1262000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">(不斷前行　不要停步)</p>
<p begin="1354400000t" end="1370400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">現在應該怎樣做</p>
<p begin="1389200000t" end="1404000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">諾曼準備要出欄</p>
<p begin="1411600000t" end="1423200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">繩子也沒有了</p>
<p begin="1428800000t" end="1450800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">艾瑪的腿又斷了，不可以行動</p>
<p begin="1451600000t" end="1469200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">艾瑪的腿很快就會康復</p>
<p begin="1476800000t" end="1497200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">繩子沒有了可以再製作</p>
<p begin="1498000000t" end="1514400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">到時就會有辦法離開這裡</p>
<p begin="1515200000t" end="1528400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">我會想到辦法</p>
<p begin="1529200000t" end="1545600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">現在首先是要救諾曼</p>
<p begin="1546400000t" end="1558000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">但是為甚麼…</p>
<p begin="1563200000t" end="1584800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">為甚麼突然要送諾曼出欄</p>
<p begin="1590800000t" end="1614400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">媽媽之前跟我說過下次出欄</p>
<p begin="1615200000t" end="1634000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">情況起了變化</p>
<p begin="1634800000t" end="1646800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">原來她說的是諾曼</p>
<p begin="1656400000t" end="1692000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">而且想不到就連修女也…</p>
<p begin="1698000000t" end="1709600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">明明中午之前</p>
<p begin="1710400000t" end="1730800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">還像平時一樣精神奕奕</p>
<p begin="1731600000t" end="1755200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">還像平時一樣笑和洗衣服</p>
<p begin="1756000000t" end="1791600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">但是現在已經不存在於這個世界上</p>
<p begin="1944000000t" end="1950400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">艾瑪</p>
<p begin="2082800000t" end="2094000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">不會有問題的</p>
<p begin="2100400000t" end="2118400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">只是沒收了繩子而已</p>
<p begin="2119200000t" end="2134400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">你在說甚麼</p>
<p begin="2135200000t" end="2155600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">我們的計劃還未結束</p>
<p begin="2156400000t" end="2169600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">你的腿也會康復</p>
<p begin="2170400000t" end="2180000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">不是這件事</p>
<p begin="2180800000t" end="2199200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">我們要阻止你出欄</p>
<p begin="2200000000t" end="2215600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">逃走計劃一定會成功</p>
<p begin="2216400000t" end="2235200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">諾曼，你也要一起逃走</p>
<p begin="2236000000t" end="2255200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">你一定要跟我們一起走</p>
<p begin="2299600000t" end="2321600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">等我一會，我去拿杯水給你</p>
<p begin="2322400000t" end="2330400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">諾曼</p>
<p begin="3150000000t" end="3169600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">阿雷，現在怎麼辦</p>
<p begin="3170400000t" end="3191200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">要不惜任何代價幫他逃走</p>
<p begin="3222000000t" end="3228400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">可惡</p>
<p begin="3272400000t" end="3299600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">阿唐、吉爾妲，開始準備</p>
<p begin="3517600000t" end="3530000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">我們幫諾曼逃走</p>
<p begin="4074400000t" end="4080000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">艾瑪</p>
<p begin="4099600000t" end="4106800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">阿雷？</p>
<p begin="4124000000t" end="4160400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">諾曼，明天中午，你一個人逃走</p>
<p begin="4161200000t" end="4187200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">我們絕對不可以讓你去送死</p>
<p begin="4198400000t" end="4223600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">對不起，我做不到</p>
<p begin="4224400000t" end="4231200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">反對…</p>
<p begin="4245600000t" end="4264000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">正確來說，明天的中午</p>
<p begin="4264800000t" end="4275200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">你一個人假裝逃走</p>
<p begin="4286400000t" end="4305600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">當我們令發訊器失效之後</p>
<p begin="4306400000t" end="4320400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">你就假裝逃走了</p>
<p begin="4321200000t" end="4337600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">在艾瑪的腿康復之前</p>
<p begin="4338400000t" end="4350000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">躲在孤兒院裡</p>
<p begin="4350800000t" end="4368400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">之後在我們實行計劃的時候</p>
<p begin="4369200000t" end="4383600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">再一起逃走</p>
<p begin="4384400000t" end="4409200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">但是如果我逃走成功</p>
<p begin="4410000000t" end="4419600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">那我逃走之後</p>
<p begin="4420400000t" end="4442400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">警備措施就會加強　　沒問題</p>
<p begin="4449200000t" end="4471600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">以這間孤兒院的飼養方針來看</p>
<p begin="4472400000t" end="4488800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">是不會高度加強警備措施</p>
<p begin="4496800000t" end="4513200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">你說飼養方針？</p>
<p begin="4514000000t" end="4540800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">第一，要輕鬆愉快、健全的飼養</p>
<p begin="4547200000t" end="4571200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">第二，要嚴格保守所有的秘密</p>
<p begin="4576400000t" end="4595600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">第一點對腦部發育來說是最適合</p>
<p begin="4602800000t" end="4617200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">輕鬆愉快地成長</p>
<p begin="4618000000t" end="4636000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">感情豐富而且健康的小朋友</p>
<p begin="4636800000t" end="4648400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">這是孤兒院製造商品</p>
<p begin="4649200000t" end="4661600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">所需的最低條件</p>
<p begin="4670000000t" end="4691200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">即是說第二點也是…</p>
<p begin="4692000000t" end="4718000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">沒錯，鬼不會主動露面</p>
<p begin="4725200000t" end="4736400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">如果以恐懼支配</p>
<p begin="4737200000t" end="4754800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">就培養不出他們想要的大腦</p>
<p begin="4762400000t" end="4776800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">如果改變警備措施</p>
<p begin="4777600000t" end="4802000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">最多只是增加巡邏人員或飼養員</p>
<p begin="4802800000t" end="4821600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">這樣的程度，總有辦法應付</p>
<p begin="4822400000t" end="4832800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">一定有</p>
<p begin="4833600000t" end="4844000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">就算是這樣</p>
<p begin="4844800000t" end="4863600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">如果他們將圍牆加高一點</p>
<p begin="4864400000t" end="4878400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">用繩子爬不上去</p>
<p begin="4879200000t" end="4903200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">下次你打算怎樣越過圍牆出去外面</p>
<p begin="4904000000t" end="4918000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">那你躲起來的時候</p>
<p begin="4918800000t" end="4938000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">偷偷地製造一條梯就行了</p>
<p begin="4938800000t" end="4955600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">那麼如果他們改造發訊器</p>
<p begin="4956400000t" end="4968800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">增強發訊器的性能呢</p>
<p begin="4969600000t" end="4995200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">就算再植入一次，我們也知道位置</p>
<p begin="4996000000t" end="5006400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">拿出來就行了</p>
<p begin="5007200000t" end="5017600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">一定會有辦法</p>
<p begin="5038800000t" end="5052400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">你明明是知道的</p>
<p begin="5053200000t" end="5075200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">總之我們就是不可以讓你去送死</p>
<p begin="5076000000t" end="5091600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">我們會準備一些糧食</p>
<p begin="5092400000t" end="5112000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">躲起來之後不可以被人發現</p>
<p begin="5112800000t" end="5134000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">加強了的警備措施總有辦法應付</p>
<p begin="5134800000t" end="5151590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">而且我手上還有可以</p>
<p begin="5152400000t" end="5167600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">阻止媽媽的殺手鐧</p>
<p begin="5168400000t" end="5182000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">你要生存下去</p>
<p begin="5182800000t" end="5207600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">就用這個方法假裝逃走　　不行</p>
<p begin="5236790000t" end="5263200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">做不到，這是不行的</p>
<p begin="5272800000t" end="5289200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">不僅是警備措施</p>
<p begin="5290000000t" end="5310000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">我逃走了的話，你或者艾瑪</p>
<p begin="5310800000t" end="5331200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">可能就會代替我被送出欄</p>
<p begin="5338800000t" end="5371600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">我絕對不會要你們當中其中一個</p>
<p begin="5376800000t" end="5390800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">代替我去送死</p>
<p begin="5405200000t" end="5416800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">我可以把性命給她</p>
<p begin="5426000000t" end="5444800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">但是其他的東西</p>
<p begin="5445600000t" end="5458400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">就一樣都不可以讓步</p>
<p begin="5466800000t" end="5488000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">我要破壞媽媽打算進行的計劃</p>
<p begin="5498000000t" end="5518400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">所以逃走計劃一定會成功</p>
<p begin="5576000000t" end="5592000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">真的很感謝你們</p>
<p begin="5598400000t" end="5618000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">至於我離開了之後的計劃</p>
<p begin="5618800000t" end="5646000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">要趁現在預先想好和決定好才行</p>
<p begin="5651200000t" end="5676800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">不要說笑了，這樣的話</p>
<p begin="5677600000t" end="5697200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">我這六年來做的事情算是甚麼</p>
<p begin="5698000000t" end="5708000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">對不起</p>
<p begin="5721600000t" end="5729200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">可惡</p>
<p begin="5778400000t" end="5800800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">那麼阿雷的腿也斷了不就行了</p>
<p begin="5810800000t" end="5837200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">挺好吧？阿雷，你把腿弄斷吧</p>
<p begin="5838000000t" end="5858800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">艾瑪，你說甚麼</p>
